# Day 08 – Cloud Server Setup: Nginx on AWS EC2

## 🚀 What I Did
- Launched EC2 instance (Ubuntu)
- Connected via SSH
- Installed Nginx web server
- Accessed server via browser
- Collected nginx logs

---

## 🛠️ Commands Used
```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install nginx -y
sudo systemctl start nginx
sudo systemctl enable nginx
curl localhost
